=E2=80=99s couch and in the
=E2=80=9CYou=E2=80=99re glib=E2=80=9D Matt Lauer interview, the meltdown wa=
s attributed within the industry as much to Cruise=E2=80=99s split from Kin=
gsley as his descent into Scientology lunacy. A few years later, Cruise=E2=
=80=99s profile was back under careful supervision=E2=80=94but by Amanda Lu=
ndberg at 42 West, Dart=E2=80=99s new startup, not by PMK. It remains with =
Lundberg today.

